* Fri Jun 19 2020 Digital-Me Infra Team <infra@digital-me.nl> - 4.0.7-1
- Rolling out version 4.0.7 - https://www.redmine.org/versions/159
- Rebuild against ImageMagick 6.9.x since 6.7.x has been remove from main repo
- Switch to Ruby 2.4 since 2.2 has been remove from sclo repo
- Update gems to date

* Wed Oct 16 2019 Digital-Me Infra Team <infra@digital-me.nl> - 4.0.1-3
- Rolling out version 4.0.1 - http://www.redmine.org/versions/145
- Reworked from Fedora to build on CentOS (7.7.1908) using rpmMake
- Use Ruby 2.2 from Software Collections (rh-ruby22)
- Bundle all required gems in 4 separated packages
- Provide config examples for each database and use it by default
- Run generate_secret_token, db:migrate and redmine:load_default_data tasks in post script
- Use standard directories for config, db, lib, log and tmp
